item.description:
Demons take on the Philly Hawks in the only Eastern League home game this year. Don't miss out on seeing the likes of big names Stratford, McCormack, Rinklin, and Evon dishing out bumps and flying high for what is anticipated to be a big clash on the rolling turf just a short dive out of town in Lexington.

Hope to see you there!
